<h2>Vital Strategies</h2>
<p>Resolve to Save Lives is housed within <a href="http://vitalstrategies.org">Vital Strategies</a>, a global health organization that works in more than 70 countries to address the world’s most challenging health issues. Resolve to Save Lives fits perfectly with Vital Strategies’ vision of a world where every person is protected by a strong public health system.</p>